陣線)の召集人Jimmy Shamが街上に攻撃された;‬<br />\nJimmy Sham, convenor of CHRF, attacked;<br />\n<br />\n陳浩天，民族黨召集人，被捕；<br />\n‪香港民族党の召集人 Andy Chanが逮捕された;‬<br />\nAndy Chan, convenor of National Party, arrested;<br />\n<br />\n鍾健平，元朗遊行發起人，遇襲；<br />\n‪元朗デモ申請者KP Chungが攻撃された;‬<br />\nKP Chung, applicant of Yuen Long march, attacked;<br />\n<br />\n民陣八三一遊行，被禁；<br />\nCHRF(民間人権陣線)が申請する8/31日のデモが却下された;<br />\nPlanned march organized by CHRF on Aug 31, banned;<br />\n<br />\n香港眾志黃之鋒、周庭，被捕。<br />\n‪香港衆志(デモシスト)の Joshua WongとAnges Chowが逮捕された;‬<br />\nJoshua Wong and Agnes Chow of Demosisto, arrested.<br />\n<br />\n香港已進入全面威權警察國家時代。<br />\n‪香港はすでに権威主義の警察国家になった。‬<br />\nHong Kong has become a full fledged authoritarian police state."},{"pid":"f7876eb3e7285612e2380daf71905d3840d1346d","tid":1517742,"uid":254729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T04:51:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae0d43db57a7f04c8439d560f9bc782bc745dcd6","tid":1517742,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:08:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mhik2fq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMhik2fq.gif&h=7b54c7c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8rnp9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=7d9a5ff5\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8rnp9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=149a0a59\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8rnp9gp%2BSv